23 

There  have  been  35  WTO  attacks  on  U.S.  anti-dumping,  countervailing  duty,  and 

safeguard (AD–CVD) law and the United States lost 33 of these cases. 

Anti-Dumping/Countervailing Duty/Safeguards Disputes 

