to  reiterate  that  we  are  right  with  you.  This  is  a  competitiveness 
issue. 

Senator  DEMINT.  What  I  hope  I  can  hear  from  you  guys  is  not 
just  pushing  Fast  Track  or  more  trade  agreements.  We’ve  go  to 
